candidates.website_content: Search this site Embedded Files Skip to main content Skip to navigation Galaxy Chihuahuas Home Available Puppies Meet the Parents Past Puppies Contact Us Galaxy Chihuahuas Home Available Puppies Meet the Parents Past Puppies Contact Us More Home Available Puppies Meet the Parents Past Puppies Contact Us Welcome to Galaxy Chihuahuas! 🌴We are located in Hawaii🌴 You can find us on Facebook, TikTok, and Instagram: Galaxy Chihuahua's WELCOME!  We have recently moved to Hawaii on the beautiful island of Oahu.  🏝️🌊 All of our puppies are raised in our home and very well socialized with people and other animals. We are a hobby breeder who cares about the overall quality of  the applehead chihuahuas and strives to breed within the AKC standard. Our goal is to raise healthy, happy, puppies with friendly temperaments. All parents are on site. Each puppy will have a full vet exam, deworming, and proper vaccinations before leaving for their new home.  Our puppies are sold as "pet only" with no papers or breeding rights.  We look forward to helping yo u find the perfect addition to your family!! FAQs Frequently asked questions: Where are you located? Makakilo, Hawaii (Oahu) How much are your puppies? Prices start at $5000 and go up.  Price depends on the individual puppy. Do you ship? No, but we can meet you at a local airport for a small fee depending on travel time. Do you have a waiting list? No. We prefer you fill out our puppy application to see if you are a good fit for one of our puppies.

 Home About Contact FAQ Pricing Canine Cardio Hawaii 
 Where Health Meets Happiness Unleash your dog's energy! Get Started Introduction Canine Cardio Hawaii LLC is Hawaii's first and only veterinary professional owned mobile dog gym! We are a Kailua based, female owned and operated, dog-powered exercise service that provides an easy and safe alternative way to exercise your dog. I come to your home and provide a fulfilling and safe workout for your dog in my fully equipped and climate controlled trailer. I am here to help the dogs of Hawai'i live a happier, healthier, and longer life through regular exercise. Canine Cardio Hawaii is where health meets happiness! What is a mobile dog gym? 
 
 
 
 
 
 
 
 
 
 
 
 
 
 
 Temperature Controlled Our trailer is equipped with cold air conditioning to ensure that your dog can exercise comfortably, no matter the weather conditions outside. 
 
 
 
 
 
 
 
 
 
 
 
 
 
 
 100% Pup-Powered Our treadmills (called slatmills) are specifically designed with dogs in mind. They are low resistance, low impact, and have no motor, so your dog can go as fast (or slow) as they want and even stop if they are tired. Safety is ensured by clipping the dogs harness to the slatmill so that they don't fall off and dogs are continuously monitored by our expert coach. 
 
 
 
 
 
 Convenient We come to you! This makes exercising your dog easier than ever. As long as there is a parking space
